[ProMED-mail thanks Jan Clement for this historical summary of detection of SEOV in the Americas and elsewhere, and its relation to a very few number of cases of human disease in the USA. Little can be added to his summary.

One hopes that his concern about lack of medical awareness of HFRS will change, and the true picture of HFRS incidence will emerge, not just in Baltimore but also in the other port cities in the USA where SEOV-related viruses have been detected in rats.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map showing the location of New York State and New York City can be accessed at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2907225,234 and a map of the USA showing the locations of the port cities mentioned, at http://www.mapsofworld.com/usa/. - Mod.TY]
